<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 28 Oct 2023 18:07:45 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>马斯克表示星链将通过援助组织支持加沙通信连接</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-28/ty-article/musk-says-starlink-will-support-gaza-communications-links-through-aid-groups/0000018b-76e3-d51e-a3cb-77ef7c900000</link><description>这位亿万富翁表示，SpaceX 将与“国际公认的援助组织”合作，为加沙提供连接，那里的电话和互联网中断导致人们与世隔绝。</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Oct 2023 16:46:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-28/ty-article/musk-says-starlink-will-support-gaza-communications-links-through-aid-groups/0000018b-76e3-d51e-a3cb-77ef7c900000</guid></item><item><title>土耳其百年诞辰黯然失色，埃尔多安在亲巴勒斯坦集会上表示：以色列是占领者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-10-28/ty-article/eclipsing-turkeys-centenary-erdogan-tells-pro-palestinian-rally-israel-is-occupier/0000018b-76ff-d2fc-adcf-f7ffb68a0000</link><description>埃尔多安邀请所有土耳其人参加集会，他说“只有我们的旗帜和巴勒斯坦旗帜会飘扬”，试图掩盖定于第二天举行的世俗共和国百年庆典</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Oct 2023 16:43:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-10-28/ty-article/eclipsing-turkeys-centenary-erdogan-tells-pro-palestinian-rally-israel-is-occupier/0000018b-76ff-d2fc-adcf-f7ffb68a0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战争暴力升级，以色列定居者杀死在约旦河西岸收割橄榄的巴勒斯坦人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-28/ty-article/.premium/settler-kills-palestinian-harvesting-olives-in-west-bank-as-violence-rises-amid-gaza-war/0000018b-769e-d4a8-a3cf-febfb9800000</link><description>自 10 月 7 日哈马斯袭击以来，约旦河西岸定居者与巴勒斯坦人之间的对抗有所增加，安全部门消息人士称此类事件损害了以色列的合法性</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Oct 2023 14:42:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-28/ty-article/.premium/settler-kills-palestinian-harvesting-olives-in-west-bank-as-violence-rises-amid-gaza-war/0000018b-769e-d4a8-a3cf-febfb9800000</guid></item><item><title>以色列左派的观念也崩溃了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-28/ty-article-opinion/.premium/the-israeli-lefts-conceptions-collapsed-too/0000018b-7253-d07a-afcf-76dbc4a00000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Oct 2023 14:34:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-28/ty-article-opinion/.premium/the-israeli-lefts-conceptions-collapsed-too/0000018b-7253-d07a-afcf-76dbc4a00000</guid></item><item><title>酒店人满为患，海滩空无一人，阳光明媚的度假城市成为因加沙战争而流离失所的以色列人的中心</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-28/ty-article/.premium/sunny-resort-city-of-eilat-becomes-hub-for-israelis-displaced-by-gaza-war/0000018b-75d9-d2fc-adcf-f7df33e00000</link><description>大约 65,000 名加沙边境社区的撤离人员已抵达埃拉特，那里的志愿者正在加紧努力，为空前的涌入者提供住房、食物和援助</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Oct 2023 11:47:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-28/ty-article/.premium/sunny-resort-city-of-eilat-becomes-hub-for-israelis-displaced-by-gaza-war/0000018b-75d9-d2fc-adcf-f7df33e00000</guid></item><item><title>加沙火箭弹击中特拉维夫附近的停车场；内塔尼亚胡会见人质家属</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-28/ty-article-live/gazans-report-heaviest-night-of-attacks-since-outbreak-of-war-as-idf-expands-ground-op/0000018b-7420-d2fc-adcf-f77f6f340000</link><description>以色列国防军司令称，战争目标需要地面行动，国防部长称战争进入“新阶段” ■ 从加沙向以色列中部和南部特拉维夫发射火箭弹 ■ 向以色列军队发射反坦克导弹后，以色列国防军和黎巴嫩军队交火 ■内塔尼亚胡会见人质家属代表，并将在战争爆发后首次接受媒体提问 ■ 埃尔多安重申哈马斯“不是恐怖组织”后，以色列下令遣返土耳其特使 ■ 自 10 月以来，至少有 1,300 人被哈马斯杀害7 ■ 哈马斯管理的卫生部：超过 6,000 名加沙人被杀，约 17,000 人受伤</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Oct 2023 04:23:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-28/ty-article-live/gazans-report-heaviest-night-of-attacks-since-outbreak-of-war-as-idf-expands-ground-op/0000018b-7420-d2fc-adcf-f77f6f340000</guid></item><item><title>加沙火箭弹击中特拉维夫公寓楼，四人受伤，其中一人重伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-28/ty-article/.premium/four-people-wounded-one-seriously-after-gaza-rocket-hits-tel-aviv-apartment-building/0000018b-7342-d2fc-adcf-f75ff7030000</link><description></description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Oct 2023 22:39:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-28/ty-article/.premium/four-people-wounded-one-seriously-after-gaza-rocket-hits-tel-aviv-apartment-building/0000018b-7342-d2fc-adcf-f75ff7030000</guid></item><item><title>集体创伤专家表示，如何治愈整个社会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-28/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/how-to-heal-an-entire-society-according-to-a-collective-trauma-expert/0000018b-72a6-d51e-a3cb-73eef93b0000</link><description>关掉电视，与孩子们一起出去玩，与朋友见面，回到自己的爱好，玩耍，最重要的是，将生活的精神层面置于中心位置。 《国土报》采访了集体创伤领域的顶尖专家纳撒尼尔·劳尔</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Oct 2023 21:28:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-28/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/how-to-heal-an-entire-society-according-to-a-collective-trauma-expert/0000018b-72a6-d51e-a3cb-73eef93b0000</guid></item><item><title>“等待伟大的灾难”：巴勒斯坦人在约旦河西岸的汽车上发现威胁传单</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-27/ty-article/.premium/wait-for-the-great-nakba-palestinians-find-threatening-leaflets-on-cars-in-west-bank/0000018b-72aa-d1da-a1bb-7fba5a020000</link><description>以色列定居者袭击他们的橄榄园后，来自约旦河西岸城镇代尔伊斯提亚的巴勒斯坦人发现挡风玻璃下夹着传单，警告他们逃往约旦，否则将被强行带走</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Oct 2023 20:12:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-27/ty-article/.premium/wait-for-the-great-nakba-palestinians-find-threatening-leaflets-on-cars-in-west-bank/0000018b-72aa-d1da-a1bb-7fba5a020000</guid></item><item><title>在哈马斯大屠杀中失去亲人的以色列和平活动人士坚守阵地</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-27/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/israeli-peace-activists-who-lost-loved-ones-in-the-hamas-massacre-stand-their-ground/0000018b-7235-d51e-a3cb-737d82d80000</link><description>哈马斯大屠杀的许多受害者及其家人过去和现在都是和平活动人士。幸存的亲属现在不仅要面对深深的悲伤和恐惧，还要面对充满仇恨的评论。但他们个人的悲剧并没有改变他们的鸽派立场。相反</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Oct 2023 19:35:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-27/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/israeli-peace-activists-who-lost-loved-ones-in-the-hamas-massacre-stand-their-ground/0000018b-7235-d51e-a3cb-737d82d80000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯正在加沙的地堡中重新调整中东的力量平衡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-10-27/ty-article/.premium/from-its-bunkers-in-gaza-hamas-is-rejiggering-the-balance-of-power-in-the-middle-east/0000018b-71a6-dec3-a59f-f5f7c1a30000</link><description>哈马斯的袭击迫使卡塔尔、沙特阿拉伯、埃及、土耳其和阿拉伯联合酋长国组成了一个不稳定的联盟。目前尚不清楚他们中的任何人是否能够拆除目前在加沙的炸弹</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Oct 2023 19:18:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-10-27/ty-article/.premium/from-its-bunkers-in-gaza-hamas-is-rejiggering-the-balance-of-power-in-the-middle-east/0000018b-71a6-dec3-a59f-f5f7c1a30000</guid></item><item><title>拜登纪念生命之树枪击事件五周年，援引以色列哈马斯大屠杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-27/ty-article/.premium/biden-marks-fifth-anniversary-of-tree-of-life-shooting-invokes-hamas-massacre-in-israel/0000018b-71eb-dec3-a59f-f5fb90f60000</link><description>拜登在匹兹堡纪念被白人民族主义者杀害的 11 名犹太人时表示，“纪念活动是在大屠杀以来对犹太人来说最致命的一天之后进行的”</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Oct 2023 18:45:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-27/ty-article/.premium/biden-marks-fifth-anniversary-of-tree-of-life-shooting-invokes-hamas-massacre-in-israel/0000018b-71eb-dec3-a59f-f5fb90f60000</guid></item><item><title>10月7日，以色列国家安全的拐点</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-27/ty-article/.premium/october-7-an-inflection-point-for-israels-national-security/0000018b-7130-d51e-a3cb-717c88f30000</link><description>哈马斯从加沙发起的进攻挑战了以色列所珍视的国防、外交政策和整个地缘政治背景的信条。以色列与伊朗的间接战争只是其后果之一</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Oct 2023 15:40:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-27/ty-article/.premium/october-7-an-inflection-point-for-israels-national-security/0000018b-7130-d51e-a3cb-717c88f30000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯官员告诉俄罗斯官方媒体，哈马斯将所有人质视为以色列人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-27/ty-article/hamas-sees-all-its-hostages-as-israelis-hamas-official-tells-russian-state-media/0000018b-716d-dec3-a59f-f57f30810000</link><description>哈马斯高级领导人：“对我们来说，所有被俘的人都是以色列人”，俄罗斯在以色列的批评中捍卫哈马斯代表团前往莫斯科是“必要的”</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Oct 2023 14:16:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-27/ty-article/hamas-sees-all-its-hostages-as-israelis-hamas-official-tells-russian-state-media/0000018b-716d-dec3-a59f-f57f30810000</guid></item><item><title>共和党总统候选人将在拉斯维加斯举行的共和党犹太人会议上讨论以色列和加沙问题</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-27/ty-article/.premium/gop-presidential-candidates-to-talk-israel-gaza-at-republicans-jewish-confab-in-las-vegas/0000018b-6b73-d326-a39b-6f7b35070000</link><description>本周末的共和党犹太联盟年度会议将由共和党总统候选人主导，他们展示了他们亲以色列的资历，或许更重要的是，他们展示了反巴勒斯坦的诚意</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Oct 2023 13:12:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-27/ty-article/.premium/gop-presidential-candidates-to-talk-israel-gaza-at-republicans-jewish-confab-in-las-vegas/0000018b-6b73-d326-a39b-6f7b35070000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军之友在坐拥巨额现金的情况下为以色列发起紧急筹款</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-27/ty-article/.premium/friends-of-idf-launches-emergency-fundraising-while-sitting-on-huge-cash-pile/0000018b-708c-d37c-a99b-f59f29880000</link><description>该组织拥有 1.74 亿美元的现金储备，但它指出，它可能不会将这些资金用于以色列与战争相关的紧急情况，因为这笔钱已经指定用于其他原因</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Oct 2023 12:26:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-27/ty-article/.premium/friends-of-idf-launches-emergency-fundraising-while-sitting-on-huge-cash-pile/0000018b-708c-d37c-a99b-f59f29880000</guid></item><item><title>美国对伊朗革命卫队成员哈马斯实施新制裁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/2023-10-27/ty-article/us-puts-new-sanctions-on-hamas-members-of-irans-revolutionary-guard/0000018b-7095-d37c-a99b-f59f79b40000</link><description>美国副财政部长在一份声明中表示，“今天的行动凸显了美国拆除哈马斯融资网络的承诺”</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Oct 2023 10:02:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/2023-10-27/ty-article/us-puts-new-sanctions-on-hamas-members-of-irans-revolutionary-guard/0000018b-7095-d37c-a99b-f59f79b40000</guid></item><item><title>身份不明的无人机在以色列和埃及边境附近的塔巴医院附近坠毁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-27/ty-article/unidentified-drone-crashes-next-to-hospital-in-taba-near-israel-egypt-border/0000018b-706b-d22c-a5ff-f36b4f6f0000</link><description>埃及军方表示，此次事件至少造成六人受伤，以色列军方称此次事件为“红海地区的空中威胁” ■ 努韦巴也发生爆炸</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Oct 2023 09:48:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-27/ty-article/unidentified-drone-crashes-next-to-hospital-in-taba-near-israel-egypt-border/0000018b-706b-d22c-a5ff-f36b4f6f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列民意调查显示，49%的人支持推迟对加沙的地面进攻</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-27/ty-article/israeli-poll-finds-49-support-holding-off-on-gaza-ground-offensive/0000018b-6faa-d1da-a1bb-6fba47b00000</link><description>近一半的受访者认为以色列应该等待在加沙的地面行动，而只有超过四分之一的受访者认为以色列国防军应该立即发动攻势</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Oct 2023 06:05:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-27/ty-article/israeli-poll-finds-49-support-holding-off-on-gaza-ground-offensive/0000018b-6faa-d1da-a1bb-6fba47b00000</guid></item><item><title>美国战斗机袭击叙利亚以回应伊朗支持组织的袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-10-27/ty-article/u-s-fighter-jets-strike-syria-in-response-to-attacks-by-iran-backed-groups/0000018b-6f8f-de3d-abdb-7fff2a110000</link><description>此次空袭发生在一周前，美国和联军部队在伊拉克和叙利亚遭到伊朗支持部队至少 19 次袭击</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Oct 2023 05:26:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-10-27/ty-article/u-s-fighter-jets-strike-syria-in-response-to-attacks-by-iran-backed-groups/0000018b-6f8f-de3d-abdb-7fff2a110000</guid></item></channel></rss>